  "detailed_description": "<h1>SUPPORTED DEVICES</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The game is fully playable on a regular desktop display.</h2></p><br><h1>Just Updated</h1><p><strong>A Big Audio and Visual Update!</strong></p><br><h1>Special Offer</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >\"You'll face some challenges with the space shuttle (no spoilers here!) during the journey. But don't panic, with a common sense you'll survive.\" - A player</h2></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Duration:</strong> Around <strong>25 minutes</strong> of action-packed gameplay, plus free exploration in the lobby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Type:</strong> Interactive <strong>musical space adventure</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Good to know:</strong> A narrative-driven space game with an immersive story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Introduction</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/cdee17152ff6e77dfa1ef1acb8660bf9.avif?t=1743681402\" width=600 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Odyssey is a story-driven space adventure for solo and multiplayer. Search for a new home for humanity while protecting your exploration ship. Scientists onboard carry Earth's last hope—its biodiversity. The fate of life itself is in your hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/3ff784bcf0b155f45ddc48e9499299fe.poster.avif?t=1743681402\" width=480 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/3ff784bcf0b155f45ddc48e9499299fe.webm?t=1743681402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/3ff784bcf0b155f45ddc48e9499299fe.mp4?t=1743681402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of an explorer and take on various tasks aboard a spaceship, all set to an uplifting musical soundscape. Navigate asteroid fields, locate and use essential tools, and protect your ship from cosmic dangers. At the end of each session, review your performance and improve your personal or social score by playing again. This multi-modal experience blends gameplay with learning, featuring a voice-acted narrative and vibrant audio to share fascinating facts about space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/244b178777a75c9ab4db6ab5fd3f2192.avif?t=1743681402\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to three explorers can embark on a journey through a post-apocalyptic universe, where Earth is no longer habitable. As a crew member aboard a massive space station, you join a team of scientists searching for a new home. The station houses isolated ecosystem bubbles, preserving Earth's last surviving plants and animals. Your mission: protect these fragile ecosystems and uncover the answers that could save humanity. The future is in your hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/106e820c687afbf50e92e9993f02feb2.poster.avif?t=1743681402\" width=412 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/106e820c687afbf50e92e9993f02feb2.webm?t=1743681402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/106e820c687afbf50e92e9993f02feb2.mp4?t=1743681402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controls</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The experience is playable on both a <strong>standard PC monitor</strong> and in <strong>Virtual Reality</strong> (tested with <strong>Oculus Rift, Windows Mixed Reality, and HTC Vive</strong>). An <strong>in-game option</strong> allows you to switch between the two modes seamlessly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the best experience, <strong>headphones are highly recommended</strong>, as the game features a rich, bass-heavy musical soundscape. While fully functional in both modes, movement controls and user interactions may vary slightly between standard and VR gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/84efea47ee77a2dec7661e5633745369.avif?t=1743681402\" width=412 height=154 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Duration:</strong> Around <strong>25 minutes</strong> of action-packed gameplay, plus free exploration in the lobby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Type:</strong> Interactive <strong>musical space adventure</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Good to know:</strong> A narrative-driven space game with an immersive story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Introduction</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/cdee17152ff6e77dfa1ef1acb8660bf9.avif?t=1743681402\" width=600 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Odyssey is a story-driven space adventure for solo and multiplayer. Search for a new home for humanity while protecting your exploration ship. Scientists onboard carry Earth's last hope—its biodiversity. The fate of life itself is in your hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/3ff784bcf0b155f45ddc48e9499299fe.poster.avif?t=1743681402\" width=480 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/3ff784bcf0b155f45ddc48e9499299fe.webm?t=1743681402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/3ff784bcf0b155f45ddc48e9499299fe.mp4?t=1743681402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of an explorer and take on various tasks aboard a spaceship, all set to an uplifting musical soundscape. Navigate asteroid fields, locate and use essential tools, and protect your ship from cosmic dangers. At the end of each session, review your performance and improve your personal or social score by playing again. This multi-modal experience blends gameplay with learning, featuring a voice-acted narrative and vibrant audio to share fascinating facts about space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/244b178777a75c9ab4db6ab5fd3f2192.avif?t=1743681402\" width=600 height=336 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Up to three explorers can embark on a journey through a post-apocalyptic universe, where Earth is no longer habitable. As a crew member aboard a massive space station, you join a team of scientists searching for a new home. The station houses isolated ecosystem bubbles, preserving Earth's last surviving plants and animals. Your mission: protect these fragile ecosystems and uncover the answers that could save humanity. The future is in your hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/106e820c687afbf50e92e9993f02feb2.poster.avif?t=1743681402\" width=412 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/106e820c687afbf50e92e9993f02feb2.webm?t=1743681402\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/106e820c687afbf50e92e9993f02feb2.mp4?t=1743681402\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controls</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The experience is playable on both a <strong>standard PC monitor</strong> and in <strong>Virtual Reality</strong> (tested with <strong>Oculus Rift, Windows Mixed Reality, and HTC Vive</strong>). An <strong>in-game option</strong> allows you to switch between the two modes seamlessly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For the best experience, <strong>headphones are highly recommended</strong>, as the game features a rich, bass-heavy musical soundscape. While fully functional in both modes, movement controls and user interactions may vary slightly between standard and VR gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/738600/extras/84efea47ee77a2dec7661e5633745369.avif?t=1743681402\" width=412 height=154 /></span></p>",
